  "1802190": {
    "name": "Puzzles For Clef",
    "steam_appid": 1802190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/1e83cb4493ab1239e19e2c2b2a598278.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=200 /></span><i>Puzzles for Clef</i> 是一款轻松的冒险游戏，是关于同名女性角色的传奇故事。在收到她姐姐 Cres 的一封信之后，我们的兔子朋友 Clef 前往她祖先的岛屿进行寻宝。旅程将带她穿越美丽、神奇和神秘的土地，探索岛上的每一个地区，解开无数谜题，发掘被遗忘已久的秘密，并重新发现她家族的遗产。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/bf5a08c34877a9b3c4e35a5da01e618b.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/e9f224b24db035d0285bb9a0bfda967b.poster.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/e9f224b24db035d0285bb9a0bfda967b.webm?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/e9f224b24db035d0285bb9a0bfda967b.mp4?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻宝是妹妹送给姐姐的生日礼物。这是一个充满魔力和神秘的世界的邀请！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索九个不同的地区，从宁静的竹林到华丽的漂浮城堡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每个地区都有自己独特的感觉和秘密等待发现！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在每个区域发现的各个谜题都是在挑战你的智慧！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/976661f7bd3e904b0fb0d8e052073de5.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/74ed4c60c743628cec7cbe225ea1ab63.poster.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/74ed4c60c743628cec7cbe225ea1ab63.webm?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/74ed4c60c743628cec7cbe225ea1ab63.mp4?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上不仅仅有 Clef 和 Cres。许多人在那里安家，他们可以与 Clef 分享私人任务。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 认识岛上的领主和他的臣子！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 许多人都准备了令人难忘的任务让 Clef 去完成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在 Clef 的整个旅行中找到当地人喜爱的各种物品。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/ccc5e6973537c5913ef59352a7eb075c.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/dc9b60ac82c8515038f2c4fb502adb9e.poster.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/dc9b60ac82c8515038f2c4fb502adb9e.webm?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/dc9b60ac82c8515038f2c4fb502adb9e.mp4?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让大钟恢复声音的旅程并不是一帆风顺的。Clef 将需要你的帮助。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 数十个谜题和密码等待解决。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每一个都设计得合乎逻辑且易于理解。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 没有欺骗性或反人类的逻辑：每项任务都具有挑战性但又让人放松，而不是令人沮丧！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/db4eecc575759c793174d17db6a181b5.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/5b05592f09000babf16ade353d716166.poster.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/5b05592f09000babf16ade353d716166.webm?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/5b05592f09000babf16ade353d716166.mp4?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >浮岛是一个充满神秘、奇迹和无尽秘密的地方。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每完成一次寻宝步骤，古岛的秘密就会慢慢揭开！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每个秘密都可能回答一个问题 - 但也可能需要解锁更多谜题来完成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索岛屿的历史和 Clef 的祖先。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/b7395abc2313a0771fe25ea460785ded.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/385e580b12c94998cde104003130375d.poster.avif?t=1767911342\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/385e580b12c94998cde104003130375d.webm?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802190/extras/385e580b12c94998cde104003130375d.mp4?t=1767911342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顺便说一下，不要担心怪物或危险。Cres 永远不会让她妹妹的生命处于危险之中。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Clef 可以在闲暇时自由探索和体验岛屿，建议多多休息！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 不用担心死亡、危险或重复出现的敌人类型 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 这只是一只兔子解谜题的游戏。</p></li></ul>",
